---
title: Dukkah-Crusted Lamb Loin with Sweet Potato Puree, Charred Chermoula Cauli and Aubergine & Dill Salsa
description: We love a good Lamb with Sweet Potato  & Aubergine and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dukkah-crusted-lamb-loin-146281bd-ca5b3869.jpg
